The Game of School (Education Policy Foundations Seminar - Capstone Experience)

Dec 10, 2018 5:00 PM - Dec 10, 2018 7:00 PM

An interactive romp through education policies, opportunities and obstacles that influence equity and excellence in education, from early childhood through college.

This will be a production with all 38 students enrolled in the master's program in Education Policy, 2018 cohort. This will be an entertaining, interactive learning experience about education policy for the TC community.
